{"tid":470004,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲俱樂部薪水支出榜：巴黎巴塞曼聯領銜，皇馬第6(內有最高人工球員一覽)","createTime":"2017-11-16T01:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T06:51:04.000Z","uid":124741,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6b468edd5d4973de0cba0be316943c5a2a427e07","tid":470004,"uid":124741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:13:12.000Z","msg":"《每日郵報》統計了歐洲俱樂部的薪水支出榜前十，球迷心中的&ldquo;土豪&rdquo;曼城和皇馬還沒進入前三，巴黎、巴薩和曼聯分列一二三位。<br />\n<br />\n注：俱樂部薪水總額按年度計算，* 代表稅後<br />\n<br />\n1 巴黎聖日耳曼2.79億英鎊（頂薪球員：尼馬週薪為53.7萬英鎊*）<br />\n2 巴塞隆拿2.64億英鎊（頂薪球員：美斯周薪為50萬英鎊）<br />\n3 曼聯2.64億英鎊（頂薪球員：普巴週薪為29萬英鎊）<br />\n4 車路士2.5億英鎊（頂薪球員：夏薩特週薪為20萬英鎊）<br />\n5 曼城2.44億英鎊（頂薪球員：阿古路周薪為22萬英鎊）<br />\n6 皇家馬德里2.4億英鎊（頂薪球員：C朗周薪為36.5萬英鎊）<br />\n7 拜仁慕尼黑2.35億英鎊（頂薪球員：利雲度夫斯基週薪為16萬英鎊）<br />\n8 阿仙奴2.1億英鎊（頂薪球員：奧斯爾、山齊士週薪為15萬英鎊）<br />\n9 利物浦2.1億英鎊（頂薪球員：古天奴週薪為20萬英鎊）<br />\n10祖雲達斯1.5億英鎊（頂薪球員：希古恩週薪為13萬英鎊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-5080981/Top-wage-bills-European-football-PSG-Barcelona.html?ITO=1490&amp;ns_mchannel=rss&amp;ns_campaign=1490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-5080981%2FTop-wage-bills-European-football-PSG-Barcelona.html%3FITO%3D1490%26ns_mchannel%3Drss%26ns_campaign%3D1490&d=HEhLnMtwE8kNTIt9u6ef2F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7d3b7328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-5080981/Top-wage-bills-European-football-PSG-Barcelona.html?ITO=1490&amp;ns_mchannel=rss&amp;ns_campaign=1490</a><br />\n<br />\n阿同利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f8c8c024d62c82e827331cd86495b9b2068209","tid":470004,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:22:36.000Z","msg":"蛆先1.5億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /